      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Michael Matheson, the Scottish Government’s Cabinet Secretary for NHS Recovery, Health and Social Care today (4<span data-fontsize="11">th</span> August ‘23) returned to his <em>alma mater</em>, Queen Margaret University (QMU), to hear how it is supporting health and social care recovery post-COVID. </p>]]></Value>
